properties.Name: AtmHoursOfOperation
properties.Description: The ATM hours of operation on a particular date at the site where it is located.

Columns.Name: AtmId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an ATM.

Columns.Description: The day of week for which the associated operation start/end hours are in effect.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate

Columns.Description: The starting or opening time of operation for the ATM.

Columns.Name: OperationEndTime
Columns.Description: The closing or ending time of operation for the ATM.

Columns.Name: AtmHoursOfOperationNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding an ATM hours of operation.
